  [*] --> APA
  APA --> PA: user accepts (gate - now also from the board via /gogo:accept, Slice C)
  PA --> IMP
  IMP --> REV
  REV --> TST
  REV --> IMP: issues (auto loop)
  TST --> IMP: issues (auto loop)
